answers.answer: Hello there! I had a similar situation happen towards the end of my pregnancy. High blood pressure or Preeclampsia  can be very serious if not watched closely. Here is a website for further infohttp://www.webmd.com/baby/tc/preeclampsia-and-high-blood-pressure-during-pregnancy-topic-overviewHope this helps!
